.Dd 2020-11-24
.Dt SLEEP 1
.Os rsUtils
.Sh NAME
.Nm sleep
.Nd suspend execution for an interval of time
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm sleep
.Ar seconds
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
utility
suspends execution for a minimum of the specified number of
.Ar seconds .
This number must be positive.
.Sh EXIT STATUS
.Ex -std sleep
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr at 1
.Sh STANDARDS
The
.Nm
utility is compliant with the
.St -p1003.1-2008
specification.
.Sh HISTORY
A
.Nm
utility appeared in
.At v4 .
